<div class="example">
  <aside class="example__info-wrapper">
    <div class="example__info-content">
      <h3 class="example__info-title">Tips</h3>
      <ul class="example__info-list">
        <li class="example__info-list-item ">
          This preview page lets you experience real-time token changes without having to start your own project.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          None of the elements is interactive. But it lets you preview the token styles.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Click the <svg class="example__info-list-item-symbol" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><circle cx="12" cy="12" fill="#0f0817" r="12"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" fill="#302c35" r="10.285714"/><path d="m11.7857145 5.14285714-5.78812399 2.55109641 5.78812399 2.54575675 5.7881244-2.54575675zm-6.21428593 10.26860026 5.86904783 2.5885426v-7.1612864l-5.86904783-2.58318751zm6.55952413-4.5727438v7.1612864l5.8690476-2.5885426v-7.15593131z" fill="#eae7ee" fill-rule="nonzero"/></g></svg> button in the bottom right corner to change the active token list.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item ">
          Change token values in <i class="example__info-semantically-different">Tokenhost 3000</i> and see updated styles applied to this page in real time. Having the browser tabs side by side helps.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Example: change <b class="example__info-important">color-interactive-primary</b> to <b class="example__info-important">tomato</b>.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Example: change <b class="example__info-important">radius-large</b> to <b class="example__info-important">36</b>.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Example: change <b class="example__info-important">color-background-surface</b> to <b class="example__info-important">transparent</b>.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Example: change <b class="example__info-important">font-size-medium</b> to <b class="example__info-important">30</b>.
        </li>
        <li class="example__info-list-item">
          Example: change <b class="example__info-important">spacing-medium</b> to <b class="example__info-important">40</b>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>🦸🏽‍♀️🦸🏿‍♂️ Superhero Cards</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <header>
      <h2 class="text-secondary"><%= Faker::Movies::StarWars.quote %></h2>
      <p class="text-tertiary"><%= Faker::Movies::StarWars.wookiee_sentence %></p>
      <button class="button-primary" id="light-theme-button">Add a Card</button>
      <button class="button-secondary" id="dark-theme-button">Ask a Question</button>
    </header>
    <section>
      <ul class="superhero-cards-wrapper">
        <% 50.times do %>
          <li class="superhero-card">
            <h3 class="text-primary"><%= Faker::Superhero.name %></h3>
            <h4 class="text-secondary"><%= Faker::Superhero.power %></h4>
            <p class="text-tertiary"><%= Faker::Address.city %></p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p><%= Faker::Books::Dune.quote %></p>
  </footer>
</div>